1
00:00:02,902 --> 00:00:04,142
Let's have a round of applause.

2
00:00:05,205 --> 00:00:05,739
What did you think

3
00:00:05,739 --> 00:00:06,573
of the film?

4
00:00:06,573 --> 00:00:07,573
Did you enjoy it?

5
00:00:08,508 --> 00:00:10,009
Did you like it? Let me hear you!

6
00:00:10,777 --> 00:00:11,778
Please welcome

7
00:00:12,212 --> 00:00:14,347
B&amp;W's Hei Yan and Bai Xing!

8
00:00:28,294 --> 00:00:29,294
Hello, everyone.

9
00:00:29,763 --> 00:00:31,230
This is your first time working together,

10
00:00:31,231 --> 00:00:33,232
yet you portrayed such an intimate

11
00:00:33,233 --> 00:00:34,400
and emotional connection.

12
00:00:34,401 --> 00:00:35,301
I have to ask,

13
00:00:35,301 --> 00:00:36,036
how did you prepare

14
00:00:36,037 --> 00:00:37,670
for such a deep, complex role?

15
00:00:38,538 --> 00:00:40,373
Well, as I've mentioned before,

16
00:00:40,774 --> 00:00:42,409
I once had feelings for someone.

17
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:43,876
So,

18
00:00:44,177 --> 00:00:45,611
I really understand that feeling

19
00:00:45,612 --> 00:00:47,813
of wanting someone but being afraid to act.

20
00:00:47,814 --> 00:00:49,982
So you drew from experience?

21
00:00:49,983 --> 00:00:51,283
I'll ask what everyone's thinking:

22
00:00:51,284 --> 00:00:52,819
Did your real-life romance

23
00:00:53,153 --> 00:00:54,120
end as happily

24
00:00:54,121 --> 00:00:55,789
as it did in the movie?

25
00:01:01,161 --> 00:01:02,729
The director's original script

26
00:01:03,029 --> 00:01:04,063
had the two characters

27
00:01:04,064 --> 00:01:05,297
reunite years later,

28
00:01:05,298 --> 00:01:06,433
only to part ways again.

29
00:01:08,067 --> 00:01:08,902
But I believe

30
00:01:08,903 --> 00:01:10,502
you should be brave when you love someone.

31
00:01:10,503 --> 00:01:12,072
Why keep it all inside?

32
00:01:15,008 --> 00:01:16,008
So,

33
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:17,142
are you saying you're the type

34
00:01:17,143 --> 00:01:18,511
to just come out and confess?

35
00:01:18,711 --> 00:01:19,711
Absolutely.

36
00:01:19,813 --> 00:01:22,215
But aren't you afraid
of losing that gamble?

37
00:01:23,316 --> 00:01:24,316
Afraid of what?

38
00:01:24,517 --> 00:01:25,517
Gambling on whether

39
00:01:25,618 --> 00:01:26,719
they feel the same way?

40
00:01:31,624 --> 00:01:32,624
No.

41
00:01:33,827 --> 00:01:35,387
I'm gambling on not having any regrets.

42
00:01:36,329 --> 00:01:38,398
That definitely deserves some applause!

43
00:01:41,534 --> 00:01:42,368
Bai Xing, you've completely

44
00:01:42,369 --> 00:01:44,169
changed my perspective of you.

45
00:01:44,170 --> 00:01:45,805
I thought you were just an idol,

46
00:01:46,106 --> 00:01:47,673
but standing here as an actor,

47
00:01:47,674 --> 00:01:48,341
you've really

48
00:01:48,342 --> 00:01:50,009
given us some words to live by.

49
00:01:50,777 --> 00:01:51,777
Bai Xing,

50
00:01:51,978 --> 00:01:53,278
can we take that

51
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:55,582
as a challenge to Hei Yan?

52
00:01:56,216 --> 00:01:57,336
Why would it be a challenge?

53
00:01:57,917 --> 00:01:59,652
Everyone has the right to choose.

54
00:02:00,687 --> 00:02:01,921
He chose silence,

55
00:02:02,155 --> 00:02:03,456
and I chose to take action.

56
00:02:03,723 --> 00:02:04,723
It's a give and take.

57
00:02:05,058 --> 00:02:06,793
Just like in the short film,

58
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:09,362
as long as one person holds on,

59
00:02:10,029 --> 00:02:11,197
that's all that matters.

60
00:02:13,066 --> 00:02:14,334
Let's hear it for them!

61
00:02:27,514 --> 00:02:28,847
Thank you to our friends in the media.

62
00:02:28,848 --> 00:02:30,649
Now, can we get a group photo?

63
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:31,851
Let's pose for a photo.

64
00:02:42,662 --> 00:02:43,862
First, let's look at the center,

65
00:02:43,863 --> 00:02:44,964
towards the cameras.

66
00:02:46,566 --> 00:02:47,300
Great. Now,

67
00:02:47,301 --> 00:02:48,902
please look to the left.

68
00:02:50,436 --> 00:02:51,537
Did everyone over there get the shot?

69
00:02:51,538 --> 00:02:52,338
And finally,

70
00:02:52,339 --> 00:02:53,339
let's look to the right.

71
00:02:54,207 --> 00:02:56,276
Listen to all those shutters clicking!
